e-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n  <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"javascript\"><code><span leaf=\"\">生成地址：<span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">https</span>:<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">//dr.miromind.ai/share/e12611c9-bcde-475b-a153-4d9aaef92fe6</span></span></code></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk3ui2f52xh\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mk3ui2femmy\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">简短总结一句话版：</span></p>\n  <h3 data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;blockquote&quot;,{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;normal&quot;,&quot;editId&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;nickname&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;authorName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;from&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" mpa-font-style=\"mk3ucz061zjo\">在目前 4080 点附近强势位置上，结合过去 20 年数据和今年政策环境，更大概率是<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">春节前围绕现在点位上下若干百分点的震荡偏强</span>，历史统计对应的大致区间大约在 4 000–4 200 点一带，但这不是预测，实际可能因突发因素大幅偏离。</span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mk3ucz061fuk\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">很有意思，MiroThinker&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">主张放弃对具体点位的精准预测。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mk3ucz061fuk\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">通过叠加历史「春节效应」统计数据与当前强劲的政策及行情趋势</span>，构建一个基于概率的合理波动区间（而非确定数值）作为投资决策的参考。</span></span></p>\n  <p class=\"js_darkmode__0\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &